Converting both numbers to base 10:
413043_{6} = 4*(6^5) + 1*(6^4) + 3*(6^3) + 0*(6^2) + 4*(6^1) + 3*(6^0) = 75103_{10}
110131_{6} = 1*(6^5) + 1*(6^4) + 0*(6^3) + 1*(6^2) + 3*(6^1) + 1*(6^0) = 31784_{10}

75103_{10} + 31784_{10} = 106887_{10}

Therefore, 413043_{6} + 110131_{6} = 106887_{10} or 1101110_{6} in base 6.